    "description": "Teamfight Royale is a competitive real-time strategy game. Assemble a team of 8 champions to fight in 1v1 arenas for dominance and control. Summon your champions carefully by strategically investing your mana to eliminate rival champions and control the battlefield. The winner will be the one who earns the most points in 5 minutes or the first to reach the maximum score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay and earn coins to recruit new champions and improve their stats, increase your team's power level for a better chance of winning battles, and rank up to the top where the masters await. You can test your composition in single-player mode while earning coins by achieving 10 victories without suffering 3 defeats.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nInvite your friends and play with them in custom mode to test your team against another player. You can adjust your composition until you find the best option or the one you're most comfortable playing with.",
